Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334580,337240}Well, good morning!\NHave you eaten your breakfast today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337240,339850}Yes, my father made it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:43.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340340,343010}Is not obstetrics difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343790,345190}Your mother is skilled.
