Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347990,351030}The night is gone and the child is not born yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353210,356390}Hey! Well okay... wait a little, do your best!
