Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428650,429700}Listen, Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430220,432760}What do you think of going to the river\Nbefore we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:18.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434180,438150}I'd like to go, but I have work in the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:24.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440320,444430}Well okay, my mom will be home\Nin the afternoon.
