Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451920,454250}No, I will not go to the river again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454480,455900}What? You don't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457000,458840}Well... it doesn't matter!
