Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522240,525040}Tell me, the child is born yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:50.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525160,530650}Yes, when your father told me the news,\NI came right away!
