Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588040,590510}But, Mom, you haven't slept last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592280,594040}Your mother is skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594220,596550}But John, can you have dinner alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598280,600320}I'll be fine, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600610,603010}Is that right? You are already a big boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:08.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604550,608380}Well, I prepared the food for you\Nand put it on the dish so you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608400,609030}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625840,627050}{\i1}Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628610,629360}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629680,631090}Hello Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:33.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631220,633960}I told you before that I can't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:37.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633960,637630}I know that! Are you going\Nto deliver the goods? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:38.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638010,638770}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639380,641390}It seems difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642150,643620}Tell me, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644110,645570}Huh? Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645570,651250}Yes, that way I can walk around\Nwith you, Colin, all over the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:56.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651980,656280}If I let you ride this bike, I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657610,661970}To move around the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661970,663940}I wonder what happens to me\Nif it's damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665190,669320}I wanted to go with Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669320,671900}I'm alone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672800,674510}{\i1}I have no other choice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690320,691950}Ah, it's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696300,701470}Amazing, I would like\Nto fly with this plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705870,707070}It's landing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729390,731090}Just awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748370,751530}Hey, stay away of this bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:36.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752070,756700}Hey don't do that! This is not mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756700,759360}Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764380,765600}This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766940,769740}How long will they continue to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778190,779910}Hey! You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779910,783050}Why are you here? This is the?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785550,788200}Don't move! You will be crushed if you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:13.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792620,793540}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:28.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805510,808090}Hey, stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810200,811670}Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816310,818530}Hey, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822200,823100}You, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824340,826620}Hey, come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:52.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829730,832700}Well... well, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834450,835170}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841420,843360}Are you okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843950,845350}Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:31.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867450,871480}Don't approach the sheep again,\Nyou will be crushed if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872150,874400}Go home quickly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876670,880820}I have to deliver these immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880950,881830}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924760,927300}Ah ah, I am tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928440,931090}I have to go home and have dinner alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935120,937730}What's the matter, hey? Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939470,941010}Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942070,943740}Don't you have a home to go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947060,949090}Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951630,954870}Cheer up... What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957460,959980}Could you be sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962380,965360}This is bad! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965550,968200}Wait, I'll take you home immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974030,977720}Colin! I finished the delivery!\NYour bike is outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978400,979350}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982570,983900}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986310,988670}Faster! Faster! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999760,1001390}Look, I lit the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002600,1004290}Come here and warm by the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:53.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007910,1013360}My mother often come back late,\Nso I know how to light it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014130,1016080}What do you think? Do you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:06.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022780,1026180}{\i1}Great smell, dinner made by my mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027460,1030630}You, could you be hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032270,1033320}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034290,1036790}This... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037170,1039150}What? There is no milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039420,1041510}Wait, I'm going to fetch milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052880,1054580}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:46.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063310,1066220}Tell me, what color is the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066220,1068550}Ah, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:52.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068550,1072990}It's covered in brown,\Nand also it has white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072990,1074390}It's this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:55.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074420,1075940}So it's still a puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078440,1081260}Listen, next time I'll see the puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081260,1082560}Well, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082560,1083660}Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084600,1085860}Take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086270,1088120}Thanks for the milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100750,1103360}{\i1}It's milk! It's delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106040,1109430}What is the matter? Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:39.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115070,1119020}What is the matter?\NCan't you drink milk by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119670,1121390}Like a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:46.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122080,1126310}I'm tired, I want my father\Ncome back quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136500,1137830}Okay here you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139890,1142060}There are two men that haven't yet ascended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142530,1143630}I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146120,1149250}Time has already passed....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150930,1153260}I hope there wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:19.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155260,1159460}What is that? It's still a puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160640,1163180}Yes, yes that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163590,1164470}{\i1}Colin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166060,1167300}Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:31.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169650,1171440}{\i1}John! Is it you, John?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171440,1172420}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173650,1176910}Sorry John, my father scolded me a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177190,1180160}Did you say "thank you" for delivery to John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180400,1182510}This is because you were busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182660,1185240}Tell me, do you have a child's bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185240,1186120}Child's bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189200,1190480}- A puppy?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191080,1194350}{\i1}Last child's bottle was sold to Mrs. Hamilton.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194760,1195840}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:00.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196580,1200890}Ah wait! I have one from my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:04.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202490,1204200}Next time I'll see the puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204200,1205060}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210090,1212220}Can it drink through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219560,1222240}You're very hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223930,1226070}You've already finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232040,1234990}What is that?\NYour mood has changed completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236600,1237990}{\i1}You feel better, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243670,1245600}I arrived late...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246470,1249330}You do extra work, Sam Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250310,1252540}No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253770,1257100}There were two men I didn't see,\Nso I rushed to look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257540,1259950}I found them relaxing inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260600,1263270}{\i1}Today Hamilton had a baby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264200,1266380}What about your child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266680,1269920}Poor one is still asleep alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270150,1273600}No, I know, I'm going to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275280,1276780}John, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277800,1278690}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279810,1282800}You wait until I get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287510,1289510}{\i1}I wonder where it came from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:43.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300230,1303720}I understand, you are no longer alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318940,1322860}{\i1}While I went to school\NI left the puppy at home, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:05.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323100,1325860}{\i1}Because of that, it brought mess in the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326610,1327930}{\i1}What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:11.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329120,1331300}{\i1}Next episode:\NA BIG MESS AT HOME{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:12.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331540,1332610}{\i1}Look forward to that!{\i0}
